title: Roll call
body:
I͟N͟V͟a͟d͟e͟r͟s͟!

Let's show Crypto who has the most active and caring community.

Our last snapshot vote got 221 votes out of 438 possible voters.
 
That's more than 50%! Great job for a 36h voting window.

-> This time we need at least 75% to prove everyone that Inverse is a DAO with an active and engaged community.
This is our Roll call vote.

**Show the world the strength of your DAO!**

_______________
*The following part is meant only for tokenholders who have 1. never voted on snapshot OR 2. never delegated to anyone OR 3. never voted themselves on-chain OR 4. never deposited into the vault with the address holding INV.*

Right now you are considered an **INACTIVE** tokenholder! 

Consider this Roll call vote here on Snapshot your last chance to prove that you care. 
This vote will last for **10 days**.
After those 10 days Inverse will take a snapshot and to find inactive tokenholders. 
Following that, an on-chain proposal will then be voted on to SEIZE your tokens.

So please, please vote here to not lose your tokens. It's FREE. It costs NO gas. 

_______
P.S: 
I might use this list to reward voters with an access token for a project I'm working on.
It's *something something* to tackle voters apathy and promote cooperation or reveal greed.

(only if we get 75%+ though - and if Nour likes the idea ;P  - still so many variables)
